BASIC INSTALLATION
------------------

If you want to install Gwiad with default options, it's simple as
make all install_server

INSTALL GWIAD AND PLUGINS
-------------------------

You can install administration plugin (to unregister plugins) with
make install_admin_plugin

If you want to install others plugins, you'll need to install Gwiad with
"make install" before compiling and installing the plugins.

TESTING GWIAD
-------------

Point your browser to http://localhost:8080 (or whatever hostname/port you have
choose in the installation process). You should see the Gwiad welcome page.

If you have install the demo with "make install_demo", then the hello
world plugin will salute you on http://localhost:8080/hello/world

